 dtestrunner nul;log;res;nl;testid
 log‚Üê''  ‚çù any messages
 res‚Üê1 ‚çù ¬Ø1: err, 0=fail, 1=ok
 nl‚Üê‚éïUCS 10

 ‚çù ids of test must follow convention
 ‚çù {id of Link tests to run}_{whatever is need to make the id unique}
 testid‚Üê2 ‚éïNQ #'GetEnvironment' 'CITA_TEST_ID'  ‚çù run basic tests
 testid‚Üê1‚äÉ'_'(‚âÝ‚äÜ‚ä¢)testid

 :Trap 0
     ‚éïSE.Link.RunTests testid
 :Case 11
     log,‚Üê'Tests failed with error',nl
     log,‚Üê(‚éïJSON ‚éïOPT'Compact' 0)‚éïDMX
     res‚Üê0
 :Else
     log,‚Üê'Tests failed with error',nl
     log,‚Üê(‚éïJSON ‚éïOPT'Compact' 0)‚éïDMX
     res‚Üê¬Ø1
 :EndTrap

 ‚éïSE.UCMD'GetTools4CITA'
 file‚Üê...
 log ‚éïSE._cita._LogStatus res
